==English==
===Noun===
'''[[mesoionic]] [[compound]]'''
#{{chemistry}} any of a class of compounds having five-membered [[ring]] [[heterocycle]]s (or their [[benzo]] derivatives) which possess a [[sextet]] of π-[[electron]]s in association with the [[atom]]s comprising the ring, but which cannot be represented by any one [[covalent]] or [[polar]] [[structure]]; typically the structure cantains a [[delocalised]] [[charge]] which cannot be associated with any one ring atom
